## R4 — MN Business Directory Sources (LOW)

Primary: Serper `/places` with MN-targeted queries (covers Google Maps listings with phone/website).

Supplemental/seed-data sources:
- **MN Secretary of State:** `mblsportal.sos.mn.gov/Business/Search` — active registered businesses, searchable by name/city. Public, no API, but scrapeable. Good for verifying active status.
- **BBB MN:** `bbb.org/search?find_loc=Minneapolis%2C+MN` — lists accredited businesses with category + contact
- **Yelp Fusion API:** free tier, 500 req/day — `GET /businesses/search?location=Minneapolis+MN&categories=bowling,hvac,dentists` — returns `name`, `url`, `phone`, `location`, `rating`, `review_count`

For the 50-lead seed dataset, use real MN business names sourced from Google Maps (Serper `/places` output). Distribute across industries: ~8 Entertainment, ~8 Pro Services, ~8 Home Services, ~8 Healthcare, ~10 Retail/Hospitality, ~8 Manufacturing/Logistics.

Real MN SMB examples for seed data:
- Entertainment: Memory Lanes (Mpls), Brunswick Zone Brooklyn Park, Pinstripes Edina
- Advertising: Periscope, Mono, Zeus Jones (all Minneapolis)
- HVAC: Genz-Ryan (Burnsville), Sedgwick Heating (Mpls)
- Dental: Dental Associates (multiple MN locations), Uptown Dental (Mpls)
- Brewery: Indeed Brewing, Fulton Beer, Surly Brewing (all Twin Cities)

